{
  "stem": "10478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- as a matter of fact, you know, and it was all known in Holland that he was planning to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we only became aware of that when they occupied Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they make propaganda with showing the, the, the movie and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had big billboards with all kinds of slogans against the Jews, Nazi [INAUDIBLE] mind, yeah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were concerned about happened to the Jews and also what's going to happen to all of us, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we have-- we all had fears that he would enter Holland, you know, and occupy Holland, and that he would do the same thing in Holland as that he did  in Germany.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- had not close connections with our neighbors, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, of course, when the occupation came, they showed to be also Nazi-friendly, yeah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nazism was, according to myself, and according to the teachings in our church, was anti-Christian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, in, in-- our church had a declaration announcing it, that anybody who became a member of the Nazi party was-- had to be dismissed and couldn't longer be a  member of the church.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That did actually happen, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of them, they resigned beforehand, because, you know, this-- that's what happens, usually.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that many, not that many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a small, little [? bit, ?] yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wasn't-- no, there was  not even a problem, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews who lived in Holland were very-- still felt at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
